Messages.Value: Thank you for calling the travel agency, my name is Elijah Martin. How can I assist you today?
Yes, hi. My name is Emily Johnson and I have a complaint about my recent trip to New York City.
Hi Emily, I'm sorry to hear that. Can you please elaborate on the issue you experienced during your trip?

Yes, I had a flight delay and when I finally arrived, my hotel room had been given away. I had to find a new hotel room at the last minute and it was much more expensive than what I had originally booked.
I'm sorry to hear that, Emily. Can you please provide me with your flight information and hotel reservation number so I can look into this issue for you?

Yes, my flight was with American Airlines, flight number AA1234, departing from Los Angeles International Airport on January 1st at 9:00am and arriving at JFK airport at 4:00pm. My hotel reservation was for the Hilton in Midtown Manhattan with reservation number 1234567 for January 1st-3rd.

Thank you for providing me with that information. I will investigate the delay with your flight and the issue with your hotel reservation. Is there anything else that you would like me to address today, Emily?
No, that's all for now. I just want this issue resolved as soon as possible.
I completely understand. I will contact you as soon as I have any updates on this situation, Emily. Thank you for bringing this to our attention and have a great day!
